Drop the scroll MP4s here:

- aries-scroll.mp4    (Aries Outdoor Living case study loop)
- aries-poster.jpg    (first-frame poster for above)
- big7-scroll.mp4     (Big 7 Construction case study loop)
- big7-poster.jpg     (first-frame poster for above)

Rendered by src/components/CaseStudy.astro from the frontmatter in
src/content/caseStudies/*.md. Missing files fall back to a "coming soon"
tile so the site never breaks — you can ship without them.

Target: ~5MB each, H.264, no audio, 1280x720, muted+autoplay+loop friendly.
